The Ultimate Florida Attraction—All in One Place!
We’re the only spot where you’ll find
mini golf, live gators, gem mining, an arcade, and go-karts
all in one unforgettable location.
Feed an alligator, explore our animal exhibits, and choose between two 18-hole mini golf courses.
Whether you’re looking for thrills or laid-back fun, we’ve got everything you need for a perfect day with friends and family.

Have Your Next Party or Event at our Location.
Celebrate at Golf N Gator!
From graduation to birthday celebration, we have the facilities and activities to make any day a special one! With a wide variety of amenities, we can keep kids, teens, and adults entertained for hours. Our party packages include mini golf parties, go-karting, arcade play, and a private party room just for your guests! We also have the Golf N Gator Mining Co., an educational wildlife show with Safari Todd, and so much more.
PACKAGES
link opening

Package 1
Includes 18-holes of Mini Golf on one of our two courses!
*Birthday child gets a free round of golf and a novelty ball of their choice.
$12 Per Person

*Birthday child gets a free round of golf and 1 Go-Kart Race.
$24 Per Person

Animals at Golf N Gator with Safari Todd
Get to know the animals at Golf N Gator with Safari Todd! He has over 20 years of large animal training experience. He has worked in various capacities at zoos, parks, and private organizations throughout Central Florida, with a focus educational programs.
Safari Todd
Go Kart Racing
Are you ready to test your skills at the Beachside Grand Prix racetrack? Our exhilarating go-kart experience is designed for fun, speed, and safety for all ages. Zip around the track in our high-performance, electric go-karts.
